column5: Hello I am looking to purchase some U40 cork seal locally if possible (local to toronto / Mississauga /Scarborough). plz let me know if you are aware of an outfitter that sells it.  thanks !
You could try John's Fly Materials in London. He's does lots of mail order buisness and I'm pretty sure he carries that product. Josh
I bought one last month at Angling Specialties
